item.title: Blowin' Off Dust
item.description: Back in 2016 my brother was running a tabletop RPG for some friends. Since they all lived in different places and couldn’t meet in-person, they used an online tabletop instead. At the time, that service had a built-in music player you could use to loop music. He made all the graphics himself in the style of an early 90s fantasy RPG, so I wrote some similarly-styled songs for him to use in-game.
